  "title": "Sales Consultant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p>• Drive and achieve monthly sales targets <br /><br />• Canvass for new customers through walk-ins and marketing & promotional campaigns such as new product launches, trade fairs, corporate events, and special programs.</p><p>• Possess cheerful and friendly personality with a high level of self-motivation.</p><p>· To be responsible and recommend customize and personalise services and products in accordance with the needs, requirements, and suitability of the customers.</p><p>· To educate and impart to customers the knowledge of maintaining and up-keeping an individual’s lifestyle and product demonstrations.</p><p>· Proactively provide after-sales support and attend to customers’ queries/complaints when necessary to maintain long-term relationships and to ensure repeated business from existing customers.</p><p>· Build long-term relationships with new and existing customers by maintaining good rapport and ensuring customer satisfaction.</p><p><strong>Job Specification:</strong></p><p>• Possess at least GCE O Level academic qualification</p><p>• Computer-literate is a MUST</p><p>• Customer-oriented with a positive attitude and initiative.</p><p>• Be responsible, trustworthy, and hardworking.</p><p>• Willing to work retail hours at Outlets.</p><p>· Preferably 1-2 years of relevant experience in the beauty and wellness industry.</p><p><strong>Job Benefits:</strong></p><ul><li>Attractive Commission Package</li><li>Up to 5 days off in a month </li><li>No OT required </li><li>Near MRT station </li></ul><p><strong>Interested candidate please WhatsApp or send a copy of your resume to 88313478. Thank you.</strong></p>",
